    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I know you say I should prioritize myself, but that's the problem isn't it? Even when I try to rest, I can see the look on my son's face when he has to help me into the chair or remind me to take my pills. It's like I'm just a permanent weight around their necks. It feels like the only way to truly stop being a nuisance and let them live their own lives is to just... not be there anymore. Does that sound crazy?",
